{"word":"G1594 - ἐκνήφω - eknḗphō - ek-nay'-fo - Awake","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκνήφω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eknḗphō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-nay'-fo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Awake</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விழித்துக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"1. to return to oneself from drunkenness, become sober"},{"paragraph":"2. to return to soberness of mind"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G3525 - νήφω - nḗphō - nay'-fo/3525\">G3525</a>; (figuratively) to <i>rouse</i> (oneself) <i>out</i> of stupor: - awake.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1594/1594\">G1594</a>, <a href=\"#/G3524/3524\">G3524</a>, <a href=\"#/G3525/3525\">G3525</a>"}]}